---
// Solution — "The Ultimate Solution For All Your Plumbing Repairs And Installations"
// Mockup: image left with floating testimonial quote card, copy + CTA right.
---

<section class="bg-surface-alt py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="container-site grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
    <!-- Image + quote card -->
    <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-lg">
      <img
        src="/images/unsplash/solution-kitchen.jpg"
        alt="Homeowner on the phone with a plumber while a pipe leaks under the kitchen sink"
        width="640"
        height="640"
        loading="lazy"
        class="aspect-square w-full rounded-[3px] object-cover"
      />
      <figure
        class="absolute -bottom-6 right-0 w-64 rounded-2xl bg-surface p-5 shadow-lg shadow-ink/10"
      >
        <blockquote class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted">
          &ldquo;PLUMBER. had a technician at our door within the hour and the
          leak fixed before lunch. Tidy, upfront, and genuinely friendly
          service.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-ink">
          Braydon Butler
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <!-- Copy -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-ink md:text-4xl">
        The Ultimate Solution For All Your Plumbing Repairs And Installations
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-prose text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted md:text-base">
        One call covers it all: leak detection and repair, fixture and
        appliance installation, drain cleaning, water heaters, and complete
        bathroom and kitchen re-plumbs. Every job is handled by a licensed
        technician, quoted upfront, and backed by our satisfaction guarantee.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#services"
        class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-ink px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-ink-soft"
      >
        Our Services
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path
            d="M5 12h14m0 0-6-6m6 6-6 6"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.8"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
